briefTitle: A Pan Asian Trial Comparing Efficacy and Safety of NN5401 and Biphasic Insulin Aspart 30 in Type 2 Diabetes
officialTitle: A Pan Asian Trial Comparing Efficacy and Safety of NN5401 and Biphasic Insulin Aspart 30 in Type 2 Diabetes (BOOSTâ„¢: INTENSIFY ALL)
summary: This trial is conducted in Asia. The aim of this clinical trial is to compare NN5401 (insulin degludec/insulin aspart (IDegAsp)) with biphasic insulin aspart (BIAsp) 30 in patients with type 2 diabetes not optimally controlled on once or twice daily insulin with or without metformin.

primaryOutcome.measure: Change in HbA1c (Glycosylated Haemoglobin) After 26 Weeks of Treatment
